Dua.

64
00:07:32,448 --> 00:07:33,448
Tiga.

65
00:07:33,728 --> 00:07:34,968
Tak apa berkedip?

66
00:07:35,208 --> 00:07:36,208
Empat.

67
00:07:38,768 --> 00:07:39,768
Lima.

68
00:07:41,368 --> 00:07:42,568
Kau sudah sampai.

69
00:07:42,648 --> 00:07:44,208
Terima kasih telah
berkendara bersama kami.

70
00:07:44,243 --> 00:07:46,003
Kau memilih untuk
membayar dengan kartu.

71
