Tapi rencana berubah.

89
00:09:09,643 --> 00:09:10,902
Diam.

90
00:09:10,992 --> 00:09:11,992
Andrey!

91
00:09:12,226 --> 00:09:12,968
Tidak!

92
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:14,559
Jangan ganggu dia! Dia hamil!

93
00:09:14,868 --> 00:09:16,890
Kami akan mengingat itu.

94
00:09:19,998 --> 00:09:20,998
Tidak!

95
00:09:22,283 --> 00:09:23,283
Jangan bergerak.

96
00:09:23,326 --> 00:09:24,443
Lakukan!

97
00:09:24,835 --> 00:09:26,309
Lepaskan celananya!

98
00:09:28,053 --> 00:09:29,514
Andrey!

99
00:09:40,392 --> 00:09:41,432
Andrey!

100
00:09:42,724 --> 00:09:44,311
Buka!

101
