Hei!

109
00:10:07,203 --> 00:10:09,557
Seseorang, tolong!

110
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:10,889
Tolong!

111
00:10:17,843 --> 00:10:19,043
Bagaimana caramu melakukan itu?

112
00:10:19,523 --> 00:10:21,643
Jadi kau ingin dia
melupakan semua itu?

113
00:10:23,003 --> 00:10:25,283
Semua terasa nyata.

114
00:10:26,963 --> 00:10:30,163
Karena itu memang nyata.
Tapi saat itu, bukan sekarang.

115
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:34,030
Di hari dia diperkosa.
/ Dia tidak diperkosa.

116
00:10:34,603 --> 00:10:36,003
Mereka tidak sempat.

117
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:40,280
Aku meminta tolong
lalu para tetangga datang.

118
00:10:41,403 --> 00:10:42,403
Dan?

119
00:10:45,883 --> 00:10:47,363
Dia kehilangan bayinya.

120
00:10:49,083 --> 00:10:50,283
Bayi kami.

121
00:10:53,443 --> 00:10:55,363
Mimpi buruk sejak itu.

122
00:10:58,283 --> 00:10:59,883
Kenapa kau tidak
memberinya waktu?

123
00:11:04,883 --> 00:11:06,803
Maaf, harusnya aku tidak kemari.

124
00:11:09,043 --> 00:11:10,403
Sebaiknya aku pergi.

125
00:11:18,772 --> 00:11:20,210
Hubungi aku saat kau siap.

126
00:11:20,241 --> 00:11:21,241
Sampai jumpa.

127
00:12:12,003 --> 00:12:13,403
Hei! / Hei.

128
00:12:14,808 --> 00:12:15,848
Konser yang bagus!

129
00:12:16,003 --> 00:12:18,923
Ya, dikemas baik malam
ini. Dengar, Andrey...

130
00:12:19,963 --> 00:12:21,443
Tolong berhenti kemari.

131
00:12:24,923 --> 00:12:28,123
Olya, boleh kita bicara?
/ Aku tak bisa lagi.

132
00:12:29,837 --> 00:12:30,735
Dengar...

133
00:12:30,963 --> 00:12:33,443
Kenapa kita tidak
mencoba terapi pasangan?

134
00:12:33,797 --> 00:12:35,637
Aku ingin berusaha. / Tidak!

135
00:13:17,710 --> 00:13:21,110
